window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>In this new edition of <i>No B.S. Marketing to the Affluent</i>, millionaire maker Dan S. Kennedy shows you how to re-position your business, practice, or sales career to attract customers or clients for whom price is not a determining factor. Learn how to sell to those who will always be spending as Kennedy shines the spotlight on the practical strategies used by The Ritz-Carlton, Disney, Harrah's Entertainment, Dove, AARP, Dr. Oz, Starbucks, Williams-Sonoma, DeBeers, the health and wellness industry, and many other fascinating and diverse true-life examples. </p> <p>You'll also discover how to: </p> <ul> <li>Use 10 surprising emotional buy triggers the affluent find irresistible </li> <li>Stop selling products and services, and learn how selling aspirations and emotional fulfillment is more profitable </li> <li>Use Kennedy's Million-Dollar Marketing System</li> <li>A step-by-step blueprint comparable to those developed for six-figure clients, ready for do-it-yourself use </li> <li>Apply the magic language of \"membership\" to any business for the affluent...from pizza shops and medical practices to retail stores and pet hotels</li> </ul>"; 
